{"tid":2182171,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇中國人普遍將蒙古帝國西征歸納為中國歷史上的功績？","createTime":"2020-08-31T06:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T02:21:43.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5759ab8c74adefa92bdce9f4b604deba2fa5759e","tid":2182171,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67br1x6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67br1x6.png&h=ecf29327&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我諗普遍中國人諗法應該同上圖一樣認為蒙古帝國係中國史，<br />\n因為元亡之後的朝代都曾在官方承認元朝係正統皇帝王朝，<br />\n蒙古帝國從在統一中原開國元朝的一刻，就理應納入為「中國」的一部份。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f5db71d85f01d58b70e3e4f4ef5bddfaa2c1ac","tid":2182171,"uid":80481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"大陸教科書係將元同其他汗國分開，元係中國歷史，其他汗國唔係"},{"pid":"e3ce7047eb986cec72af5302781defa8b1b82f5c","tid":2182171,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f5db71d85f01d58b70e3e4f4ef5bddfaa2c1ac","tid":2182171,"uid":80481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"大陸教科書係將元同其他汗國分開，元係中國歷史，其他汗國唔係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:32:27.000Z","msg":"忽必烈去左大都建元之後，哈刺和林搞既忽里勒台大會無請到忽必烈，咁你話蒙古人有無當元係蒙古既一部分？"},{"pid":"8c2c9af2b0d2f4efc5a079c8884e24975d3a02e3","tid":2182171,"uid":184726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"蒙古得 咁日本都得啦"},{"pid":"e2a323ed6d36163ddd4971f837212cf1e44b4ae6","tid":2182171,"uid":97080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c2c9af2b0d2f4efc5a079c8884e24975d3a02e3","tid":2182171,"uid":184726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"蒙古得 咁日本都得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"日本都得咁鄭和既美洲都得喇"},{"pid":"afb19f578baf7db5599a5ef679ba6ec202171310","tid":2182171,"uid":111934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,